WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:01.990
Good morning, family. How are y'all

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.070
doing today? I have some things on

00:00:04.080 --> 00:00:05.829
my heart, but first off, let's give God

00:00:05.839 --> 00:00:09.270
some praise. For the Lord is good and

00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:13.430
his mercy endures forever.

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:24.790
Father, I

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:27.269
thank you that you endure forever and

00:00:27.279 --> 00:00:29.830
your mercy is new every morning. Great

00:00:29.840 --> 00:00:31.910
is your faithfulness to me, oh God.

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:33.430
Thank you, Father, for all that you're

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:36.150
going to do today. I ask

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:38.630
you, Father, to anoint this broadcast,

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:41.350
this video today, and this YouTube

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:43.990
video. I thank you, Father, that you

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:45.510
speak through my vocal cords and you

00:00:45.520 --> 00:00:47.190
think through my mind. None of me and

00:00:47.200 --> 00:00:50.229
all of you, in the mighty name of Jesus.

00:00:50.239 --> 00:00:52.790
I thank you, Father. I have an

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:55.910
urgency in my heart for what's coming

00:00:55.920 --> 00:00:58.310
and to tell the people that Jesus is

00:00:58.320 --> 00:00:59.349
coming.

00:00:59.359 --> 00:01:03.430
Well,

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:06.149
this is what I have for y'all today. I

00:01:06.159 --> 00:01:08.149
was driving down the road and the

00:01:08.159 --> 00:01:11.109
Lord just decided to speak. I mean, the

00:01:11.119 --> 00:01:13.670
prophetic unction just hit me hard.

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:15.590
Like I said, I do not

00:01:15.600 --> 00:01:18.149
consider myself a prophet, but

00:01:18.159 --> 00:01:20.550
when I pray, I see visions and the

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:23.270
Lord shows me things to come.

00:01:27.040 --> 00:01:29.350
He showed me Israel,

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:31.590
and I saw

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:34.550
a major event about to take place in

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:39.030
Israel. I saw at this time people in the

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:42.149
streets with prayer

00:01:42.149 --> 00:01:42.159
shawls

00:01:42.159 --> 00:01:44.630
like what I have. They had these prayer

00:01:44.640 --> 00:01:47.190
things,

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:50.310
they had the Israeli flag, and

00:01:50.320 --> 00:01:51.990
they had it over their shoulders, kind of

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:53.830
like what they do at a

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:55.429
sporting event, but they had it like

00:01:55.439 --> 00:01:57.190
this and it was draped around them.

00:01:57.200 --> 00:02:00.149
They were celebrating in the streets,

00:02:00.159 --> 00:02:02.630
saying, "The

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:05.030
deliverer has come. The deliverer

00:02:05.030 --> 00:02:05.040
has come."The

00:02:05.040 --> 00:02:07.190
women were dancing in the

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:09.270
streets and the men were dancing, and

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:11.589
they were celebrating

00:02:11.599 --> 00:02:17.190
some kind of victory. I do not know

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:19.830
what this was, if it was war or whatever.

00:02:19.840 --> 00:02:22.070
All I know is they were

00:02:22.080 --> 00:02:24.710
celebrating something that had happened in

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:28.550
the streets in Israel. I saw rabbis.

00:02:28.560 --> 00:02:32.790
I saw Orthodox Jews with their hats on

00:02:32.800 --> 00:02:36.229
with curls and

00:02:36.239 --> 00:02:40.309
long beards, and they were weeping

00:02:40.319 --> 00:02:43.589
at this sight, at this

00:02:43.599 --> 00:02:45.910
experience. They were rocking at the

00:02:45.910 --> 00:02:45.920
Wailing

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:47.910
Wall. I could see them praying

00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:49.910
and weeping at the Wailing

00:02:49.920 --> 00:02:52.150
Wall, and I could see them throughout the

00:02:52.160 --> 00:02:54.710
streets. I saw

00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:58.550
them actually say, "We've been in error.

00:02:58.560 --> 00:03:00.630
We have been in error in some of our

00:03:00.630 --> 00:03:00.640
teachings."The

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:03.430
Holy Spirit had gotten a

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:07.030
hold of them and they were

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:09.110
telling the people—I saw them

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:10.869
teaching and telling the people that

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:12.550
they had been in error about some

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:14.149
things and they were going back and

00:03:14.159 --> 00:03:16.309
correcting things that they had been

00:03:16.319 --> 00:03:19.509
teaching that were in error. I saw a

00:03:19.519 --> 00:03:23.830
glory explosion over the Jewish people.

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:28.149
A mighty revival started to break out

00:03:28.159 --> 00:03:30.949
in the streets in Jerusalem and all of

00:03:30.959 --> 00:03:33.589
the other areas of Israel. They were

00:03:33.599 --> 00:03:36.630
breaking forth in a revival

00:03:36.640 --> 00:03:39.430
of healings and demonstrations and

00:03:39.440 --> 00:03:42.630
manifestations of the glory. And the

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:45.750
Lord said, "I'm going to become real to

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:49.589
this generation like I had been in the

00:03:49.599 --> 00:03:52.070
past with the children of Israel when

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:54.070
they were delivered out of the hand of

00:03:54.080 --> 00:03:58.309
Egypt. I'm going to do another wave of

00:03:58.319 --> 00:04:01.910
my presence, of my glory, over this

00:04:01.920 --> 00:04:05.509
generation, and they will see that I am

00:04:05.519 --> 00:04:08.470
real and that I am their Messiah,

00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:12.470
that I am God to

00:04:12.470 --> 00:04:12.480
them."The

00:04:12.480 --> 00:04:17.349
Lord showed me a great and mighty wave

00:04:17.359 --> 00:04:20.949
of his presence

00:04:20.959 --> 00:04:23.670
over all of the people. But

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:25.749
they were delivered from something.

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:27.590
Like I said, I do not know what this

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:29.749
was about, but they were dancing in the

00:04:29.759 --> 00:04:32.390
streets. I could see

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:35.270
the rabbis and

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:37.670
the tears that were flowing. There

00:04:37.680 --> 00:04:39.830
was a heavy-set man, and I don't

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:42.070
know who this man was, but he had

00:04:42.080 --> 00:04:44.950
chubbier, heavier cheeks and

00:04:44.960 --> 00:04:47.909
a longer, silvery-peppered beard.

00:04:47.919 --> 00:04:50.310
I could see gray in his beard.

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:53.110
He was a rabbi, and he had glasses on

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:55.830
and he was rocking. I remember

00:04:55.830 --> 00:04:55.840
seeing

00:04:55.840 --> 00:04:57.909
these curls,

00:04:57.919 --> 00:04:59.350
but I could see the

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:00.390
people and they were teaching that "we

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:02.230
were erring in our ways,"and they knew

00:05:02.240 --> 00:05:03.670
that they were corrected about some

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:04.710
things. I just thought it was

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:06.629
amazing in this visitation.

00:05:06.639 --> 00:05:08.870
The Lord just told me that

00:05:08.880 --> 00:05:10.390
he was going to become real, and I don't

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:11.830
want to keep rehashing that, but I'm just

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:13.830
going back over my mind, remembering

00:05:13.840 --> 00:05:18.310
everything I was shown.

00:05:18.320 --> 00:05:22.710
Then the Lord showed me this. He said,

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:25.270
"Brandon,

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:27.749
I'm going to uncap

00:05:27.759 --> 00:05:32.150
the wells of revival in

00:05:32.150 --> 00:05:32.160
America."And

00:05:32.160 --> 00:05:34.950
he said to me, "The great healing

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:38.469
revivals that took place in the 1930s

00:05:38.479 --> 00:05:41.510
and 40s—you know, the tent revivals back

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:45.670
whenever A. A. Allen, Jack

00:05:45.670 --> 00:05:45.680
Coe,

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:48.870
William Branham, Smith, not

00:05:48.880 --> 00:05:53.590
Kenneth Hagin, but you know, John

00:05:53.600 --> 00:05:56.790
G. Lake, that era of ministers."He told

00:05:56.800 --> 00:05:59.189
me Aimee Semple McPherson, and it goes on

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:02.629
and on. He said, "Those wells were

00:06:02.629 --> 00:06:02.639
capped."People

00:06:02.639 --> 00:06:04.790
have wondered, "Where has

00:06:04.800 --> 00:06:07.189
that gone?"They were capped. I looked up

00:06:07.199 --> 00:06:09.909
what the word

00:06:09.909 --> 00:06:09.919
'capped'means.

00:06:09.919 --> 00:06:12.469
What does it mean to cap a well? The

00:06:12.479 --> 00:06:15.590
wells that are no longer being used but

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:18.710
might be needed in the future can be

00:06:18.720 --> 00:06:22.150
sealed with a cap that covers the top of

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:25.590
the well casing pipe to prevent

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:29.270
unauthorized access and contamination.

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:32.950
A cap is a temporary

00:06:32.960 --> 00:06:35.749
groundwater protection solution that

00:06:35.759 --> 00:06:38.790
allows a well to be used at a later

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:42.230
time. He brought up the scripture

00:06:42.230 --> 00:06:42.240
in

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:45.350
Genesis

00:06:45.350 --> 00:06:45.360
and

00:06:45.360 --> 00:06:47.590
he was talking about

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:49.909
Isaac bringing forth the old wells that

00:06:49.919 --> 00:06:52.150
Abraham had dug, that the

00:06:52.160 --> 00:06:53.830
Philistines put dirt on and

00:06:53.840 --> 00:06:56.070
filled up, and

00:06:56.070 --> 00:06:56.080
capped

00:06:56.080 --> 00:06:59.189
those wells off.

00:06:59.199 --> 00:07:01.670
But the Lord was showing

00:07:01.680 --> 00:07:04.950
me that he's

00:07:04.960 --> 00:07:09.270
uncapping those wells of revival.

00:07:09.280 --> 00:07:12.390
He's uncapping all those

00:07:12.400 --> 00:07:16.309
deep wells. I was driving by Tulsa,

00:07:16.309 --> 00:07:16.319
ORU,

00:07:16.319 --> 00:07:23.670
and I saw the glory. I

00:07:23.670 --> 00:07:23.680
started

00:07:23.680 --> 00:07:29.990
crying again. I

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:34.070
saw the glory over the Mabee Center, and I

00:07:34.080 --> 00:07:36.390
saw the glory of the Lord over there

00:07:36.400 --> 00:07:43.270
again,

00:07:43.280 --> 00:07:46.870
and those old wells of revival from

00:07:46.870 --> 00:07:46.880
Oral

00:07:46.880 --> 00:07:49.350
Roberts and the greats that

00:07:49.360 --> 00:07:51.749
walked this land before and have

00:07:51.749 --> 00:07:51.759
gone

00:07:51.759 --> 00:07:53.909
home to be with the Lord. He said, "I'm

00:07:53.919 --> 00:07:56.790
going to do it one more time, and I'm

00:07:56.800 --> 00:07:58.869
bringing forth a great revival again,

00:07:58.869 --> 00:07:58.879
son."Those

00:07:58.879 --> 00:08:01.589
old wells that have been

00:08:01.599 --> 00:08:04.950
capped for protection because the season

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:06.710
was over for that, he said, "I'm

00:08:06.720 --> 00:08:09.749
bringing forth those great wells again,

00:08:09.759 --> 00:08:10.950
and I'm going to use

00:08:10.960 --> 00:08:17.350
you and I'm going to use these people

00:08:17.360 --> 00:08:19.749
for great healings. Demonstrations

00:08:19.759 --> 00:08:22.790
and manifestations of my glory will be

00:08:22.800 --> 00:08:25.749
seen again. I'm going to touch this

00:08:25.759 --> 00:08:29.510
generation one more time."I told you,

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:32.870
he said, "There's one more call. One

00:08:32.880 --> 00:08:35.670
last call."And I've asked him because

00:08:35.680 --> 00:08:36.949
people were arguing with me and saying,

00:08:36.959 --> 00:08:38.870
"Oh, there's no great revival. That's

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:41.909
not in the Bible in the last

00:08:41.909 --> 00:08:41.919
days."Well,

00:08:41.919 --> 00:08:44.310
I was out there and I said, "Lord,

00:08:44.320 --> 00:08:46.630
what do you say to this?"And he said,

00:08:46.640 --> 00:08:50.949
"Brandon, who's in control of

00:08:50.949 --> 00:08:50.959
time?"He

00:08:50.959 --> 00:08:54.470
said, "I am. Were you there

00:08:54.480 --> 00:08:57.910
when I threw the stars into space?

00:08:57.910 --> 00:08:57.920
Were

00:08:57.920 --> 00:09:00.150
you there when I created the heavens

00:09:00.160 --> 00:09:03.350
and the earth?"He was

00:09:03.360 --> 00:09:05.509
referring to Job whenever he was talking

00:09:05.519 --> 00:09:09.910
to Job.

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:12.790
He said, "Brandon,

00:09:12.800 --> 00:09:16.150
my heart is the harvest.

00:09:16.160 --> 00:09:19.990
My heart is the harvest.

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:23.110
One last call, son. I'm calling in the

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:26.310
sheep from the back of the fold.

00:09:26.320 --> 00:09:28.870
One last call. I'm calling them forth to

00:09:28.880 --> 00:09:32.310
come home, giving them an

00:09:32.310 --> 00:09:32.320
opportunity."And

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:35.110
in this, I'm going to uncap those

00:09:35.120 --> 00:09:38.710
great wells of revival.

00:09:38.720 --> 00:09:42.310
And I saw at this time a vision of tents

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:46.790
full of people again. I saw tents and

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:49.910
brush harbor churches again. He showed

00:09:49.920 --> 00:09:54.310
me a revival of fire like what Azusa Street

00:09:54.320 --> 00:09:56.070
had.

00:09:56.080 --> 00:10:00.550
I'm so hungry for this.

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:03.269
The glorious church in Collinsville,

00:10:03.269 --> 00:10:03.279
Oklahoma—he's

00:10:03.279 --> 00:10:04.949
going

00:10:04.949 --> 00:10:04.959
to

00:10:04.959 --> 00:10:31.110
use this place.

00:10:31.120 --> 00:10:32.949
He's going to use Branson, Missouri.

00:10:32.959 --> 00:10:34.710
He's going to use these places. And

00:10:34.710 --> 00:10:34.720
he

00:10:34.720 --> 00:10:36.230
told me, "Those that are hungry

00:10:36.240 --> 00:10:38.389
and thirsty after righteousness, they

00:10:38.399 --> 00:10:41.590
will be filled with my

00:10:41.590 --> 00:10:41.600
glory."He

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:45.190
said, "I want you to go back and I

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:48.470
want to speak to you about Rosh Hashanah

00:10:48.470 --> 00:10:48.480
to Rosh Hashanah."This

00:10:48.480 --> 00:10:52.310
time, he

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:55.030
said, "This is the beginning of the

00:10:55.040 --> 00:10:58.710
glory. This is the beginning of what you

00:10:58.720 --> 00:11:02.150
have waited for for so

00:11:02.150 --> 00:11:02.160
long."He

00:11:02.160 --> 00:11:04.310
talked about

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:07.829
a great harvest of souls coming from Rosh Hashanah

00:11:07.829 --> 00:11:07.839
to Rosh Hashanah.

00:11:07.839 --> 00:11:11.269
You will see

00:11:11.279 --> 00:11:13.910
first the blade, then the ear, and then

00:11:13.920 --> 00:11:16.310
the corn. Concerning this, the

00:11:16.320 --> 00:11:18.470
greater harvest of the glory that you

00:11:18.480 --> 00:11:22.710
have wanted for so long will come: first

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:25.030
the blade, then the ear, and then the

00:11:25.040 --> 00:11:27.990
full corn. You will see it.

00:11:32.800 --> 00:11:34.550
He said, "This is a time of

00:11:34.560 --> 00:11:38.310
refreshing, a time of surrender, a time

00:11:38.320 --> 00:11:42.389
of rest, a time of healing, a period to

00:11:42.399 --> 00:11:45.269
fully let go and prepare for the new

00:11:45.279 --> 00:11:47.590
cycle

00:11:47.600 --> 00:11:51.990
ahead."He

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:53.509
talked about the Democratic

00:11:53.519 --> 00:11:55.430
Party and the evil over the United

00:11:55.440 --> 00:11:57.990
States of America. There will be an

00:11:58.000 --> 00:12:02.630
event that will shake the USA

00:12:05.600 --> 00:12:08.389
out of a fear to control; they

00:12:08.399 --> 00:12:12.230
will lose control, is what the Lord said.

00:12:12.240 --> 00:12:14.949
He said

00:12:14.949 --> 00:12:14.959
seedtime

00:12:14.959 --> 00:12:17.590
and harvest

00:12:17.600 --> 00:12:22.069
will have come to its fullest.

00:12:22.079 --> 00:12:24.629
You will see this happen.

00:12:24.629 --> 00:12:24.639
Seedtime

00:12:24.639 --> 00:12:27.670
and harvest will come to its

00:12:27.680 --> 00:12:30.550
fullest in these days

00:12:30.560 --> 00:12:33.670
ahead. The seeds they

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:36.310
have sowed in the past will come to

00:12:36.320 --> 00:12:39.110
harvest finally at last.

00:12:39.120 --> 00:12:41.430
Then he started

00:12:41.440 --> 00:12:44.949
talking to me about a great humbling. A

00:12:44.959 --> 00:12:48.230
great humbling will come, an uprising;

00:12:48.240 --> 00:12:50.870
there will be weeping, and they

00:12:50.880 --> 00:12:53.350
will be very sad. People will say,

00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:57.110
"What did we do?"You will see

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:04.629
an exposing of great

00:13:04.639 --> 00:13:06.470
darkness

00:13:06.480 --> 00:13:09.829
in the Democratic Party. And when this

00:13:09.839 --> 00:13:12.710
happens, the very snake they thought

00:13:12.720 --> 00:13:16.790
they controlled will turn on them. I

00:13:16.800 --> 00:13:19.829
saw that big python that I told you all

00:13:19.839 --> 00:13:23.430
about in the past

00:13:25.440 --> 00:13:27.590
lashing out, striking, striking,

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:29.430
striking. It was striking them.

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:34.870
I saw an exposing. I saw

00:13:34.880 --> 00:13:37.350
embarrassing moments coming from

00:13:37.350 --> 00:13:37.360
Kamala

00:13:37.360 --> 00:13:39.990
Harris. I saw things that were done in

00:13:40.000 --> 00:13:43.750
the past that she thought she had buried

00:13:43.760 --> 00:13:46.710
and were no longer a problem

00:13:46.720 --> 00:13:49.110
resurfacing. There

00:13:49.110 --> 00:13:49.120
were

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:54.310
several incidents

00:13:54.310 --> 00:13:54.320
of

00:13:54.320 --> 00:13:57.509
things that were dirty, things that were

00:13:57.519 --> 00:14:00.470
very embarrassing to the point where

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:03.430
I heard her saying, "I

00:14:03.440 --> 00:14:05.670
should have never ran. I should have

00:14:05.680 --> 00:14:07.590
never put my foot in this,"because

00:14:07.590 --> 00:14:07.600
they

00:14:07.600 --> 00:14:10.629
were very humiliating.

00:14:10.639 --> 00:14:13.990
I saw very

00:14:14.000 --> 00:14:18.310
